Examples.Code:
$CssProperties = @{
    'background-color' = 'lightblue'
    'border' = @{
        'style' = 'solid'
        'width' = '1px'
        'color' = 'black'
    }
}
ConvertTo-CascadingStyleSheets -Css $CssProperties -Name '#myDiv' -WithTags

Converts the CSS properties into a CSS stylesheet with the selector '#myDiv' and includes CSS style tags.
